Release
LTS.403.2
of March 15, 2024
New features
For user to get identified in the System, it’s now possible to setup integration with some external authentication providers.
A new getExternalUserProviderContext is added to receive information on user signing in with an external authentication provider.
A possibility to configure column titles for the "Table" analytical panel was added.
Changes and improvements
Improvements in working with registry objects with possibility of multiselect;
Stabilizations in importing reporting form templates;
New possibilities in exporting dashboard charts in .pdf format;
It’s now possible to add ETL schema stage without default value;
Improvements in running business processes;
Changes in viewing notification templates according to the given layout and links operability;
Improvements in viewing object name according to visual settings;
Stabilizations in viewing object profile attribute groups according to the given settings;
Improvements in viewing "Status bar (Advanced)" widget stage names;
Updates in viewing system buttons at the registry control panel;
Updates in color changing for all menu item icons using design settings;
Page loading stabilizations;
Improvements in multidomain authorization;
Stabilization in working with compiled algorithms with the "text" function used;
Optimizations in registry object filtering;
Updates in viewing panels on the object profile according to the given settings;
The list of message reactions was updated in the GreenData Messenger.
